text: Ordered only their sambal stingray. Was flavourful and the meal is chunky. First time being served with a thick layer of stingray. Juicy and nice. Many seafood stall over here, a lucky pick
BBQ stingray was so good we ordered it twice. Prawn paste chicken was delicious
Food was nice. Very reasonably priced. Served with a smile. I think this shop is currently very underrated!
They should improve on their stingray sauce. But their stingray was still plump and juicy. Lala were fresh and sweet. Their prices were still reasonable.
